Package: Rmultifractional
Type: Package
Title: Simulation and analyses of multifractional processes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andriy Olenko, Nemini Samarakoon 
Maintainer: Nemini Samarakoon <NWijesingheS@ltu.edu.au> 
Description: Simulation of the Guassian Haar Based Multifractional Process (GHBMP). Analyses includes estimation of the Hurst function, clustering multifractional processes based on the Hurst functions and several functions to compute and plot characteristics of the processes.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: parallel (>= 4.2.2), parallelly (>= 1.37.1), ggplot2 (>= 3.5.1), zoo (>= 1.8-12), matrixStats (>= 1.2.0), proxy, rlang, stats, foreach, doParallel, plotly, shiny
LazyData: false
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
